Alannah Hill broke her foot after shooing her dog and hitting skirting board . 
 Doctor noticed a freckle on her foot and she was diagnosed with cancer . 
 Another three months it would likely have spread and become terminal . 
 Hill has had part of her toe removed and a skin graft from her inner thigh . 
 She prides herself on her alabaster skin - even going to the extremes of wearing gloves and using a parasol to protect her from the sun . 
 